| Detection 2: Credential Dumping - NPPSpy and cmdkey (T1003)
| Trigger: NPPSpy DLL installation or cmdkey credential listing
| Severity: Critical
| ATT&CK: T1003 - OS Credential Dumping

index=main source="WinEventLog:Microsoft-Windows-Sysmon/Operational"
| rex field=_raw "CommandLine'>(?<CommandLine>[^<]+)"
| rex field=_raw "Image'>(?<Image>[^<]+)"
| search CommandLine="*NPPSpy*" OR CommandLine="*cmdkey*"
| table _time, Image, CommandLine
| sort _time
